txt.en: Searched many ornate coffers in Durthang.
Ornate coffers can be found in Durthang; the possessions of Ugrukhôr's Black Númenórean retinue.
You ransacked a number of the ornate coffers found in Durthang. You can say at least that the Black Númenóreans in Ugrukhôr's retinue will make no use of their contents.
Ornate coffers can be found in Durthang; the possessions of Ugrukhôr's Black Númenórean retinue. Even if there is nothing of value to you in there, it is still best that they don't have it.
Ransack the ornate cofffers throughout Durthang, in Udûn.
